<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Coventry Hills</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A typical suburban neighborhood of Calgary, Coventry Hills is located within the north-west quadrant of the city and is represented by the Ward 3 Councilor in the Calgary City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A dynamic and highly urbanized neighborhood, the community in Coventry Hills enjoys a centralized location within the heart of the city with all of the major public amenities and recreational venues located at a walking distance from all the dwellings in the area.</p>
        </div>
